@1069 = ~Rifthome Axe +2~
@1070 = ~These items are vexing to modern sages, since their creator remains completely unknown. Its markings are vaguely dwarven, but no dwarf yet encountered on Faerûn has claimed a kinship with the mysterious smith, and further investigations are met with gruff explanations and eventually stony silence. This has caused some to speculate that it may not be the product of a terrestrial dwarven hand, but rather of some extraplanar variant. Dwarves laugh this off, of course, claiming the maker likely has no time for nosey scholars.

