To honor those warriors who accomplish great deeds within the ranks of the Purple Dragon Knights, King Azoun IV had the Royal Magician Vangerdahast create several of these belts. His daughter, Alusair, now continues that tradition, occasionally offering these belts to entice proven adventurers into joining the ranks of the Purple Dragons.

