@1386 = ~Nymph Cloak~
@1387 = ~Named for the creatures most closely associated with beauty, Nymph Cloaks are popular fodder for tavern tales among the common folk. The story usually involves some hapless noble couple spending a fortune on one or more such items so they can stand to look at one another. It always gets a big laugh among a copper-ale crowd, though most professional bards consider such pandering a tool of the unskilled.

STATISTICS:

Special Abilities:
 Blinding Beauty (1x per day): blinds opponents within 20' for 1 turn (save vs. spell at -2 neg.)

