@1424 = ~Cloak of Protection +3~
@1425 = ~The Protector
The royal guard of King Pyronan, ruler of Impiltur, were given cloaks such as this as an honorary show of status. Unfortunately, members of the guard had trouble coming to a consensus amongst themselves regarding who should receive such cloak. After years of internal hostility, the mantles were lost and the guards were replaced by less greedy individuals.

Cespenar infused this cloak with even more powerful protective enchantments.

