@1443 = ~Fullen Woolspinner, an ambitious halfling from a well-to-do family, left his home to spend several years adventuring. During his travels, he ended up staying with a family of dwarven weaponsmiths. Much impressed by their throwing axes, which always returned to the hands of their wielder, Fullen sought to make a dagger that could do the same. With the help of his dwarven friends he succeeded, creating several of the famous Fullen Boomerang daggers.

