@1768 = ~Protection from Cold~
@1769 = ~This scroll protects its user from all cold-based attacks, whether magical or non-magical in origin. All of the damage from attacks such as icy dragon breath will be absorbed, and the user will become completely immune to the effects of spells such as Ice Storm and Cone of Cold. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off after 5 turns.

Requires: 10 Intelligence
Not Usable By:
 Wizard Slayer~
@1770 = ~Protection from Electricity~
@1771 = ~This scroll protects its reader from all electricity-based attacks, whether magical or non-magical in origin. All of the damage from attacks such as electrical dragon breath will be absorbed, and the user will become completely immune to the effects of spells such as Lightning Bolt, Glyph of Warding, Call Lightning, and Chain Lightning. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off after 5 turns.

Requires: 10 Intelligence
Not Usable By:
 Wizard Slayer~
@1772 = ~Protection from Fire~
@1773 = ~This scroll protects its reader from all fire-based attacks, whether magical or non-magical in origin. All of the damage from attacks such as fiery dragon breath will be absorbed, and the user will become completely immune to the effects of spells such as Burning Hands, Agannazar's Scorcher, Fireball, Flame Strike, and Fire Storm. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off after 5 turns.

Requires: 10 Intelligence
Not Usable By:
 Wizard Slayer~
@1774 = ~Protection from Magic~
@1775 = ~This scroll creates a very powerful globe of anti-magic in a 3' radius around the reader. No form of magic can pass into it or out from it, and any spell effects currently affecting the target will be removed. The globe cannot be dispelled, nor breached by most anti-magic attacks, but a Spellstrike spell can destroy it. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off after 5 turns.

Requires: 10 Intelligence
Not Usable By:
 Wizard Slayer~
@1776 = ~Protection from Ailments~
@1777 = ~This scroll will protect the reader from all forms of poison and disease, be they of a natural or magical nature. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off after 5 turns.

Requires: 10 Intelligence
Not Usable By:
 Wizard Slayer~
@1778 = ~Protection from Undead~
@1779 = ~This scroll creates a magical barrier around the reader at a distance of one foot. The barrier moves with the recipient and protects him from all forms of attack made by undead creatures. The recipient is immune to level drain effects, attacks made by undead creatures against the user receive a -2 penalty to THAC0, and any saving throws caused by such attacks are made by the user with a +2 bonus. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off after 5 turns.

Requires: 10 Intelligence
Not Usable By:
