@2223 = ~Dak'kon's Zerth Blade +2~
@2224 = ~This sword was the weapon of choice of the famous githzerai Dak'kon who was killed by a powerful entity while working for a creature known as the Nameless One. Perhaps the strange circumstances of his death preserved this blade, as it would otherwise have lost its form when his will no longer shaped it.

