This flail was created a century ago to commemorate the defeat of the demon Belhifet. It was meant to remain within the town of Easthaven to remind the people of the great evil that had barely been defeated, but it was stolen, only to reappear years later on the northernmost reaches of the Sword Coast, in the City of Sails.

