@2430 = ~Manual of Bodily Health~
@2431 = ~A typical manual of bodily health provides the reader with valuable information regarding preventative medicine, basic first aid, and proper muscle toning. As if this isn't enough, the manual is also magically enhanced, thereby allowing an individual to raise their Constitution by a single point. Unfortunately, the manual will disappear after a single use.

