@2438 = ~A typical tome of clear thought contains a collection of esoteric and scholarly literature, often involving obscure mathematical or algebraic formulae or the occasional reference to inter-planar biology. Such tomes are usually magically enhanced, thereby allowing an individual to raise their Intelligence by a single point. Unfortunately, the manual will disappear after a single use.

